text: Goephanes niveoplagiatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1894.Biolib.cz - Goephanes. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Goephanes Category:Beetles described in 1894 Category:Taxa named by Léon Fairmaire
